{"tid":2078994,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【守身如玉】黃夏蕙接戲有底線 堅持不拍被強姦戲","createTime":"2020-06-25T12:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T14:50:06.000Z","uid":71085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"baa282338f06595f919c0d881937d26b498457b6","tid":2078994,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbS5xjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbS5xjz.png&h=ff13d594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWtHzxY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWtHzxY.png&h=99a88e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙和經理人Simon合作近10年，打造夏蕙BB近年極盡騎呢路線，今日二人應邀到銅鑼灣接受節目《關公有約》訪問，夏蕙姨原來經常遲到激嬲經理人，又試過初相識時Simon竟然叫夏蕙姨參加派避孕袋活動，她說：「我當期時話咁老都派得，好尷尬，未見過呢啲嘢又冇用過，覺得好肉酸，後來知道幫到年輕人唔使有BB，又可以乾淨啲。」兩人合作至今有不成文底線，不會接拍被強姦角色，夏蕙姨說：「只要唔傷害人就得，做豬做狗都做過，過年時瞓棺材都照去。」<br />\n<br />\n免login一click即睇：<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200625&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=61096753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200625%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D61096753&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QffUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=d69cb98e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200625%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D61096753&h=5c3e5949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200625&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=61096753</a>"},{"pid":"d38e9aa26c93426f11a9a0df141975e56b4c8e99","tid":2078994,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"佢吃過幾多鮮肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98bfa35e133742f64a8cb6fd0d189f551f5be33","tid":2078994,"uid":71085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d38e9aa26c93426f11a9a0df141975e56b4c8e99","tid":2078994,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"